Implementation planned for follow-up commits:

- **REST server** — Axum router with `GET /api/snapshot`, `POST /api/patch`, `GET /api/knobs`, `POST /api/knobs/batch`.
- **Swagger UI** — `utoipa`-generated OpenAPI spec served at `/docs`.
- **MCP server** — `mcp-protocol-sdk` stdio transport exposing tools: `read_config`, `update_config`, `list_knobs`, `get_snapshot`.

#### Integration

**`scriptbots-app/src/lib.rs`** — Exports shared types:

